description: The 90s produced some great rock music, and this playlist is packed with acoustic covers of the finest 90s rock songs. Featuring acoustic versions of tracks by Nirvana, Red Hot Chili Peppers, Pearl Jam, Oasis, Foo Fighters, Alice in Chains, REM, Radiohead, Soundgarden, Stone Temple Pilots and more.
